title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1985-06-15
lineage: Transfer: Master Cassette > Nakamichi CR7a playback with no dolby > Korg mr2000 (1 bit, 5.6 Mhz). Render from 1 bit to 24 48 wave file using AudioGate.  Pre dolby nr decode eq and software dolby B decode using Nuendo and DDICodec.
source: Source: Nakamichi 300 shotguns > Sony TC-D5M > Master Cassette (Maxell MX90s, Dolby B On) Location: Taper section; stand 6 to 7 feet high.
